Interface Tree<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the objects stored in this tree
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MyTree

    public interface Tree<E>
    Position based multi-way tree. Children are always reached via the iterator interface
    Author:
    ps
